       &none             &kp LEFT      &kp UP            &kp RIGHT       &kp PAGE_UP      &kp LEFT_BRACKET  &mmv MOVE_LEFT   &mmv MOVE_UP       &mmv MOVE_RIGHT  &kp RIGHT_BRACKET
       &kp LEFT_COMMAND  &kp LEFT_ALT  &kp LEFT_CONTROL  &kp LEFT_SHIFT  &kp PAGE_DOWN    &none             &kp RIGHT_SHIFT  &kp RIGHT_CONTROL  &kp RIGHT_ALT    &kp RIGHT_GUI
&none  &none             &none         &kp DOWN          &none           &none            &none             &none            &mmv MOVE_DOWN     &none            &none              &none
